<div class="blogentry">

<p>QuirksMode.org is the prime source for browser compatibility information on the Internet.
It is maintained by Peter-Paul Koch,
<a href="/about/">mobile platform strategist</a> in Amsterdam, the Netherlands.</p>

<p>QuirksMode.org is the home of the <a href="/compatibility.html">Browser Compatibility Tables</a>,
where you&#8217;ll find hype-free assessments of the major browsers&#8217; CSS and JavaScript
capabilities, as well as their adherence to the W3C standards.</p>

<p>It is also increasingly the home of <a href="/mobile/">ground-breaking mobile web research</a>.</p>

